      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a reliable companion. It's in really solid shape and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for someone looking for a great deal on a car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today. It has a few minor signs of love from over the years, but it\u2019s been well-cared for and is looking for a new home. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
