    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS. This example utilizes the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, providing tactile engagement and direct control over the variable M differential. The chassis has been addressed with rear subframe reinforcements, ensuring structural rigidity under high lateral loads. It rides on a tuned suspension with refreshed bushings, offering neutral handling characteristics and sharp turn-in. The engine maintains strong compression across all cylinders and pulls cleanly to the 8,000 RPM redline. A driver-spec machine with sorted mechanicals and a focused performance pedigree.",
